            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德康醫療(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DXCM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DXCM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DXCM-US</a>)截至台北時間12日23:44股價上漲3.4美元，報70.80美元，漲幅5.04%，成交量3,003,613（股），盤中最高價70.80美元、最低價65.96美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.29%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.09%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.04%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>德康醫療(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DXCM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DXCM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DXCM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.37%</li> <li>近 1 月：-2.23%</li> <li>近 3 月：+3.5%</li> <li>近 6 月：-19.16%</li> <li>今年以來：+1.29%</li></ul></section></main>",
